Major News Items in Leading Kenyan Newspapers
NAIROBI , November 15 ( Xinhua ) -- The following are major news items in leading Kenyan newspapers Sunday :
Kenya Times :
-- Smuggling and criminal activities along the common borders of Kenya and Uganda have declined in the face of joint security operations by the two countries , Busia District Commissioner Ezekiel Machongu has said .
Daily Nation :
-- South African President Nelson Mandela is to make a one-day visit to Tanzania Tuesday , during which he is expected to bid farewell to Tanzanian leaders and receive a hero 's medal .
-- Kenyan President Daniel arap Moi has sent a special message to his Ugandan counterpart Yoweri Museveni reportedly on Uganda 's intent to sell additional power to Kenya .
